"{\"uid\": \"attitude.co.uk-life-tom-daley-tests-out-beds-in-paris-olympic-village-470105\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"HomeNewsNews Sport  23 July 2024  ByBrian Leonard  Tom Daley has celebrated his arrival at Paris 2024 by testing out the infamous beds in the Olympic Village.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 158, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 51, \"end\": 60, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Daley\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.469496902075688e-22, \"text\": \"Tom Daley\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Daley\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Daley\"}, {\"begin\": 142, \"end\": 157, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\", \"score\": 0.9999999998283329, \"rank\": 1.7155583932428154e-10, \"text\": \"Olympic Village\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The star had better get comfortable, as this is where he will be staying for the next three weeks.\", \"from\": 160, \"to\": 258, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Paris Olympics take place from Friday 26 July to Sunday 11 August 2024.\", \"from\": 259, \"to\": 334, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The cardboard 'anti-sex' beds were introduced at the 2020 Olympics in Tokyo, supposedly to discourage sex between athletes and restrict the spread of Covid-19.\", \"from\": 336, \"to\": 495, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 406, \"end\": 411, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9998898722453717, \"rank\": 0.00011011921868731357, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"For those wondering about the cardboard beds in the village, I am going to show you what they look like,\\\"the divertold fans on TikTok yesterday (22 July 2024).\", \"from\": 497, \"to\": 657, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 625, \"end\": 631, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/TikTok\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0228910567842905e-23, \"text\": \"TikTok\", \"types\": [\"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/TikTok\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/TikTok\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"This is cardboard,\\\" the 30-year-old continued.\", \"from\": 659, \"to\": 706, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"As you can see, it's like a box.\", \"from\": 707, \"to\": 740, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Then you have got the mattress.\", \"from\": 741, \"to\": 772, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Then these cardboard boxes, here, like so, with the mattress on top, and a mattress topper.\", \"from\": 773, \"to\": 864, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"And we get our own little Paris 24 [bedspread].\\\"\", \"from\": 866, \"to\": 915, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Later in the video, Tom is seen jumping up and down.\", \"from\": 917, \"to\": 969, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"And as you can see, they are pretty sturdy!\\\"\", \"from\": 970, \"to\": 1015, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"he adds, as he poses on all fours, giggling.\", \"from\": 1016, \"to\": 1060, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The way you went straight into that all-fours position,\\\" commented one Tom fan on the Instagram version of the video.\", \"from\": 1062, \"to\": 1180, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1149, \"end\": 1158, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.2418473362881018e-17, \"text\": \"Instagram\", \"types\": [\"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Assume the position!\\\"\", \"from\": 1182, \"to\": 1203, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"joked a second.\", \"from\": 1204, \"to\": 1219, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"That pose at the end was no accident!\\\"\", \"from\": 1220, \"to\": 1259, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"a third furthermore added.\", \"from\": 1260, \"to\": 1286, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Why the beds have made a reappearance is unclear, as there is no ban on sex between athletes at the Olympics, according to reports.\", \"from\": 1288, \"to\": 1419, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"M\\u00e9lissa Chovino, a spokesperson for the Paris 2024 organising committee, recently toldSELF\\\"there was no intimacy ban in Tokyo [either], but rather health restrictions linked to COVID.\\\"\", \"from\": 1421, \"to\": 1605, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1461, \"end\": 1471, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999999998647127, \"rank\": 1.3530103463474403e-10, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 1541, \"end\": 1546, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9998898722453717, \"rank\": 0.00011011921868731357, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A post shared by Tom Daley (@tomdaley)  \\\"Paris 2024 is not imposing, nor have we been asked to implement, any restrictions in this regard,\\\" Chovino added.\", \"from\": 1607, \"to\": 1761, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1624, \"end\": 1633, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Daley\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.469496902075688e-22, \"text\": \"Tom Daley\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Daley\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Daley\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Ilona Maher, a Team USA rugby player, meanwhile said that International Olympic Committee is \\\"not policing what people are doing in the village.\\\"\", \"from\": 1763, \"to\": 1908, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1763, \"end\": 1774, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ilona_Maher\", \"score\": 0.9999999134149713, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Ilona Maher\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ilona_Maher\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ilona_Maher\"}, {\"begin\": 1778, \"end\": 1786, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.6968147911682641, \"rank\": 0.43201879905074386, \"text\": \"Team USA\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 1821, \"end\": 1852, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"International Olympic Committee\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We are glad to hear it!\", \"from\": 1910, \"to\": 1933, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00a9 2025 Stream Publishing.\", \"from\": 1935, \"to\": 1960, \"entities\": []}]}"